OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPost Office confirms boss  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fis under investigation     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Post Office has confirmed that its 
OL,6, current boss, Nick Read, is under      
OL,7, investigation, after its former        
OL,8, chairman Henry Staunton shocked MPs by 
OL,9, making the revelation.                 
OL,11,FMr Staunton was at a hearing to discuss
OL,12,Fcompensation payments to               
OL,13,Fsub-postmasters at the centre of the   
OL,14,FHorizon scandal.                       
OL,16,FAlan Bates, who inspired an ITV drama  
OL,17,Fon the issue, told MPs the government  
OL,18,Fshould "get on and pay people".        
OL,20,FThe investigation is ongoing.          
